{"tid":1569182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[反思反省]兄弟爬山，各自努力","createTime":"2019-09-14T13:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T15:30:13.000Z","uid":7484,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f486db2bbe6729f34760594534737f096abed8d8","tid":1569182,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:46:32.000Z","msg":"6月9日 個日我行到夏愨道有義士叫人一起出去佔路，個時無人理佢，我個fd 都叫我行啦 6月9日 多人但最後都無人佔路無人理個位手足 仲有人話佢係鬼<br />\n<br />\n個日佔唔到路 唔係因為人少係因為周圍既人話佢係鬼<br />\n<br />\n當時我都咁諗，仲覺得佢 on9<br />\n回想番我覺得好對唔住依位手足<br />\n我先係on9<br />\n<br />\n所以我之後都係寧願到現場先算，睇下有咩幫到手，就算咩都做唔到都去左先<br />\n<br />\n話唔好去淘大既人就係左膠都係敵人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567877\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567877</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我標題唔好對唔住，我反省，但唔想不分化，所以係到回應一下<br />\n<br />\n去到就淨係拉你，有咩著數？<br />\n你喺邊？現場相認？<br />\n有腦都知唔係宜家去<br />\n有邊次開po要人要人係救到手足你講<br />\n明知死黑警淨係拉我地手足， 咁點解要去比藍絲打之後就比人拉， 你解釋下<br />\n樓主心聲：繼續送頭就啱<br />\n有狗你博咩<br />\n樓豬冇腦<br />\n樓豬係黑警，勿推<br />\nSir 你死左全家味？<br />\n樓主咁勇有冇去現場呀<br />\n樓主去左還拖未<br />\n又有狗，又有藍絲，明顯係個局。除咗送頭仲有咩用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我希望大家回想一下721當日 先有成千白衫人係元朗舉牌，但人理<br />\n之後先有幾百人無差別攻擊西鐵站市民<br />\n最後係手足到場先趕返佢哋入村<br />\n今日你唔理d 籃衫人 唔等於佢地會就咁算<br />\n佢地可能會周街打人，今日淘大商場你叫人唔好去幫，他日你屋企商場出事，你係咪叫人唔好去幫<br />\n<br />\n運動至今係街頭我地一向處於下風，我地唔係有勝算先去，係為咗爭取一絲嘅勝算，為之前犧牲被捕既義士行落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後如果我係 警察 籃絲 三毛 我死全家絕子絕孫<br />\n<br />\n聽日見"},{"pid":"b336dc86124d10d57d7b164c0ccbb7d418bcf5ac","tid":1569182,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:47:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f49f89fa7b4895fb456293ae643eea577e34026","tid":1569182,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:47:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f69bd6451f890d1bc72c11d0549182892d79298","tid":1569182,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36aa8e21bf4bc2b1c951c172cb569a91ba3d4a6f","tid":1569182,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:48:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8717f41f1c649f85ffb901c88e64249f612df48","tid":1569182,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:49:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95734b887ca9fcb2cf30120a8b194d7ac242c16d","tid":1569182,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:50:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50c19edadca41197081359aeed143dbf0fcf5363","tid":1569182,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:51:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a206b5e3729f005c411781ec7d9b723a7038ca5","tid":1569182,"uid":175091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:51:51.000Z","msg":"連登對幫拖、拉開左膠已有共識<br />\n但諗到有個盲點係唔睇連登既和理非，為數不少，我地要係fb推多d呢個思想"},{"pid":"eb3c50dc6ebdfbcb6b43a82524b09e06c55ed7ce","tid":1569182,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:52:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7b4c2afb504f9a6b61da95361a30736cc49f3bd","tid":1569182,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:53:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f48c0443a6e2555f53a2e998bd804a2c53143a2e","tid":1569182,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply